textBox.richText: “Good job guys! Thanks to everyone who cheered and swam! We deserved first place and it’s all down to you guys! You were the reason why we won swimming gala, and I want us to keep going and take that energy and house spirit into sports day! This is my last big event as student leader so thanks for making my last swimming gala an amazing one, and a successful one!” -Mervyn McKinley, Head of House
